The '''"Twenchok" foil''' was a [[foil]]&mdash;a type of [[Sword/Legends|sword]]&mdash;made by the [[Barnax]]. [[Mlatar Thon Gra]] used a "Twenchok" as one of the three constituent parts of [[Cene Gilvent]]'s customized weapon, the [[Soknar]].<ref name="AIR">''[[Alliance Intelligence Reports]]''</ref>

